Field Detail

person

private java.lang.String person
The Person data for this request.

requestReference

private java.lang.String requestReference
A request reference number. This is not normally supplied by the original client when making the request. But it is supplied to the server when the request is delivered to the server. It may also be specified by the caller in order to associate a request with an earlier request.

destinationAddress

private java.lang.String destinationAddress
Address of the destination to send this request to. In most cases this is null because the OEC library will determine the request destination address based on the request type. However in the case of a proactive notification of revised person information, the requester may specify where to send the revised person data.

destinationName

private java.lang.String destinationName
Name of the destination to send this request to. In most cases this is null because the OEC library will determine the request destination address based on the request type. However in the case of a proactive notification of revised person information, the requester may specify where to send the revised person data.

matchAlgorithm

private java.lang.String matchAlgorithm
Match algorithm to use. One of the following values:

Normal - Do a normal, weighted match
FingerprintMustMatch - Like normal except only return results where fingerprint is above the fingerprint match confidence threshold.

If not specified, the default is Normal.
